1. *Bolju* odluku treba doneti što pre. (A better decision should be made as soon as possible).
2. Znam da postoji *bolja* mogućnost. (I know that there is a better option).
3. On je znao da će se stvari promeniti na *bolje*. (He knew that things would change for the better).
4. Uradiću sve što je u mojoj moći da stvari budu *bolje*. (I will do everything in my power to make things better).
5. Ona je verovala da će biti *bolja* budućnost. (She believed that there would be a better future).